== 個人生活 ==
韋比曾經是一名[[警長|警長]]<ref name="UEFA">{{Cite web |url=http://www.euro2008.uefa.com/MultimediaFiles/Download/PressConference/Competitions/MediaServices/68/51/03/685103_DOWNLOAD.pdf |title=2008年歐洲足球錦標賽 傳媒資料 |accessdate=2008-06-24 |archive-date=2008-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080602221739/http://www.euro2008.uefa.com/MultimediaFiles/Download/PressConference/Competitions/MediaServices/68/51/03/685103_DOWNLOAD.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在2011年新年因為其在足球上的貢獻而被受勳[[大英帝國勳章|大英帝國員佐勳章]]（MBE）。<ref>{{London Gazette |issue=59647 |date=31 December 2010 |startpage=23 |supp=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-12090365 |title=New Year Honours for Lennox, Suchet, Hancock and Webb |accessdate=2012-01-25 |archive-date=2016-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529221135/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-12090365 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

韋比於2013年4月回到[[南約克郡|南約克郡]]警察局。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.southyorks.police.uk/news-syp/top-referee-returns-police-force-work-young-people-football-initiative|title=Top referee returns to police force to work with young people on football initiative|publisher=South Yorkshire Police|access-date=16 February 2017|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809195553/http://www.southyorks.police.uk/news-syp/top-referee-returns-police-force-work-young-people-football-initiative|dead-url=no}}</ref>

韋比於2021年4月與同為警察的德國籍女裁判[[毕碧安娜·施泰因豪斯|毕碧安娜·施泰因豪斯]]結婚。<ref>{{cite web |title=Referees Howard Webb and Bibiana Steinhaus marry |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/56734091 |publisher=BBC Sport |access-date=13 April 2021 |date=13 April 2021 |archive-date=2021-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414101753/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/56734091 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

